item.title: Takeaways from Lenovo Techworld India Edition
item.author: thinkuldeep@gmail.com (Kuldeep Singh)
item.description: Lenovo, the global technology leader, hosted the India edition of its flagship event, Tech World , on March 16th, 2023. Industry leaders come together and peep into the future of smarter technology, that is empowering a changing world through innovative products, solutions, and witness technological solutions. I get a chance to join the event, and meet and listen to the industry leaders, experience lenovoâ€™s innovative product line, and see breakthroughs in india shaping up.
